from turtle import  Turtle
#functions
def square(name,length):
    name.fd(length)
    name.right(90)
    name.fd(length)
    name.right(90)
    name.fd(length)
    name.right(90)
    name.fd(length)
    name.hideturtle()
    
def rectangle(name,length):
    name.fd(length)
    name.left(120)
    name.fd(length)
    name.left(120)
    name.fd(length)
    name.hideturtle()

#create new turtle
sq1 = Turtle()

#making a square
square(sq1,200)

#making a rectangle
rectangle(sq1,200)
